{"tid":543072,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"支那斥日機場唱國歌國民「激化矛盾」","createTime":"2018-01-28T06:27:09.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-28T07:26:18.000Z","uid":6604,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"14f42cbf5add8c30450b710786672d797599bbfd","tid":543072,"uid":6604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-28T06:27:09.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://s.nextmedia.com/apple/a.php?i=20180128&amp;sec_id=15335&amp;s=0&amp;a=20287733華斥日機場唱國歌國民「激化矛盾」\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Fapple%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20180128%26sec_id%3D15335%26s%3D0%26a%3D20287733%E8%8F%AF%E6%96%A5%E6%97%A5%E6%A9%9F%E5%A0%B4%E5%94%B1%E5%9C%8B%E6%AD%8C%E5%9C%8B%E6%B0%91%E3%80%8C%E6%BF%80%E5%8C%96%E7%9F%9B%E7%9B%BE%E3%80%8D&d=xl%2FLXOVrUJasthmZibJTJ0%2FDJpISyAq9ELy6OyFxwDc%3D&h=465516e9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Fapple%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20180128%26sec_id%3D15335%26s%3D0%26a%3D20287733%E8%8F%AF%E6%96%A5%E6%97%A5%E6%A9%9F%E5%A0%B4%E5%94%B1%E5%9C%8B%E6%AD%8C%E5%9C%8B%E6%B0%91%E3%80%8C%E6%BF%80%E5%8C%96%E7%9F%9B%E7%9B%BE%E3%80%8D&h=e321efcf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://s.nextmedia.com/apple/a.php?i=20180128&amp;sec_id=15335&amp;s=0&amp;a=20287733華斥日機場唱國歌國民「激化矛盾」</a><br />\n<br />\n175名支那乘客因廉航延誤，高唱國歌大鬧日本成田機場事件餘波未了。日多家媒體報道事件，並用「騷動」、「支那人暴行」等語句形容。支那外交部也出聲批國民，指集體唱國歌方式不合適，易挑起民族感情對立甚至激化矛盾；更稱國人出境「不能事事都依賴政府」。<br />\n<br />\n支那外交部領事保護中心參贊趙岩表示，這是一件乘客和航空公司普通糾紛，用集體唱國歌的方式解決問題顯然不合適，反而易挑起民族感情對立，甚至激化矛盾。趙稱，每年有近1.4億支那人出境，遇到一些意想不到的事太正常，國民不能事事依賴政府，這不是一個成熟大國公民的心態。<br />\n<br />\n此外，日本外相河野太郎昨起訪華3天，今日將與支那外長王毅會談。日媒指他會提出支那潛艇在尖閣諸島（支那稱釣魚島）毗連海域航行問題，籲早日啟用日支軍方的海空聯絡機制。另外針對支那要求在支外企交納社保養老金問題，河野將向支方交涉要求減免，涉在支工作約7萬名日系企業外派人員。河野此行還希望就進一步改善日支關係，力爭早日舉行日支韓首腦會談，並實現日本首相安倍晉三與支那國家主席習近平的互訪。在應對強行實施核與導彈開發的朝鮮方面，河野還希望確認就切實履行制裁展開合作的方針。這是河野首次以外相身份訪支。"},{"pid":"84a65e73f27a1e2f388c12963d803ef511855d72","tid":543072,"uid":55732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-28T06:38:50.000Z","msg":"m巾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ea12b055ccbe191c655335a82a24843eaee5b28","tid":543072,"uid":21035,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-28T06:46:22.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">更稱國人出境「不能事事都依賴政府」</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/28/144613_4b8faa2d6d8a836ff5694f7999775485.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F28%2F144613_4b8faa2d6d8a836ff5694f7999775485.png&h=2780aa23&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ff1607df7e214095f21c9ffe69acc756d03fe664","tid":543072,"uid":3241,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"2ea12b055ccbe191c655335a82a24843eaee5b28","tid":543072,"uid":21035,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-28T06:46:22.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">更稱國人出境「不能事事都依賴政府」</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/28/144613_4b8faa2d6d8a836ff5694f7999775485.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F28%2F144613_4b8faa2d6d8a836ff5694f7999775485.png&h=2780aa23&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-28T06:48:20.000Z","msg":"領事館六日冇人聽， 非辦公時間冇人聽<br />\n入去咩都計左錢先 咁垃圾領事服務都係支那獨有"},{"pid":"149890ff0cb1388210f64bd321b88664813fdc62","tid":543072,"uid":48796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-28T07:23:38.000Z","msg":"成篇文都係支那 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ae5a509b7113ae082b6684ce6fa1de1564e9399","tid":543072,"uid":98659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-28T07:26:18.000Z","msg":"支那人暴行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.